nder-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/live-sam-fender-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/live-sam-fender-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/live-sam-fender-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《<a href="https://nme-next.netlify.app/artists/the-war-on-drugs">毒品战争</a>》的亚当·格兰迪尔（Adam Granduciel）开放了与即将发行的专辑中的“音乐秀”山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）合作的。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/sam-fenders-people-watching-review-3812982">山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）的“观看人”是英国最好的讲故事者之一的巨大回报</a></strong></li></ul><p>Fender将于2月21日通过Polydor（<a href="https://samfender.lnk.to/peoplewatching" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预享用</a>）发行他的第三张专辑“ People Watch”。该唱片是由Fender与他的乐队成员Dean Thompson和Joe Atkinson，制片人Markus Dravs和Granduciel一起制作的。</p><p> “十七岁的歌手” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-teases-new-music-with-the-war-on-drugs-adam-granduciel-3601247">首先暗示他在三月份与音乐家合作</a>，与制片人，工程师和其他音乐家一起在美国的录音室共享录像。</p><p>从十月开始的进一步更新中，他取笑了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-teases-new-album-is-finished-and-mastered-3799886">新专辑已经完成并“掌握”</a>了Granduciel的意见，此后，他与<a href="https://guitar.com/news/music-news/adam-granduciel-sam-fender-war-on-drugs-people-watching/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Guitar.com</em></a>谈论了这一过程。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCUcrKRtqKY/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: fl